17:49.369 --> 17:52.239
Whoa! There's poo
coming out now!

17:55.508 --> 17:56.476
Jesus.

17:58.545 --> 18:01.414
It's spinning its
[BLEEP] wheels in sixth!

18:06.453 --> 18:08.821
This is frightening,
that's what it is.

18:11.324 --> 18:14.161
Whoa! More poo.

18:14.161 --> 18:18.331
I didn't think it was possible
to shit yourself to death.

18:23.903 --> 18:25.805
[CHUCKLES]

18:31.711 --> 18:35.182
The grip is genuinely
incredible.

18:39.419 --> 18:42.021
Oh, there you go.

18:42.021 --> 18:45.192
