naughty car!

19:06.879 --> 19:08.481
Jesus.

19:10.550 --> 19:12.852
This recalibrates
your mind.

19:12.852 --> 19:16.088
I didn't think anything
could be as exciting
as that Porsche,

19:16.088 --> 19:18.691
but this-- this is.

19:18.691 --> 19:21.294
